<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/seo-head', { seo }) %>
<body class="seo-body">

  <%- include('partials/seo-header') %>

  <section class="seo-hero">
    <div class="seo-hero-inner">
      <nav class="seo-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span>›</span>
        <a href="/tour-packages">Tour Packages</a><span>›</span>
        <span><%= pkg.name %></span>
      </nav>

      <div class="seo-badge"><%= pkg.badge %> · <%= pkg.type %></div>
      <h1 class="seo-hero-title"><%= pkg.name %></h1>
      <p class="seo-hero-sub" style="font-size:1.15rem; color: var(--brand-gold)"><%= pkg.subtitle %></p>
      <p class="seo-hero-sub">🗓️ <strong><%= pkg.duration %></strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Starting from <strong><%= pkg.pricing && pkg.pricing[0] ? pkg.pricing[0].price : 'Call for quote' %></strong></p>

      <div class="seo-hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+919785307799" class="seo-cta-primary">📞 Book This Package</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919785307799?text=Hi%2C%20I%20want%20to%20book%20the%20<%= encodeURIComponent(pkg.name) %>%20package." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="seo-cta-secondary">💬 WhatsApp Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-section" style="background: #0f0f1a;">
    <div class="seo-container seo-two-col">

      <div class="seo-main-col">

        <div class="seo-card">
          <h2>About This Tour</h2>
          <p><%= pkg.description %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="seo-card">
          <h2>Tour Highlights</h2>
          <ul class="seo-highlights-list">
            <% pkg.highlights.forEach(function(h) { %>
            <li>✓ <%= h %></li>
            <% }); %>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="seo-card">
          <h2>Day-by-Day Itinerary</h2>
          <div class="itinerary-list">
            <% pkg.itinerary.forEach(function(day) { %>
            <div class="itinerary-day">
              <div class="itinerary-day-label"><%= day.day %></div>
              <div class="itinerary-day-body">
                <h4><%= day.title %></h4>
                <ul>
                  <% day.activities.forEach(function(act) { %>
                  <li><%= act %></li>
                  <% }); %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="seo-card">
          <h2>What's Included</h2>
          <ul class="seo-includes-list">
            <% pkg.inclusions.forEach(function(inc) { %>
            <li>✓ <%= inc %></li>
            <% }); %>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="seo-card">
          <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="seo-faqs">
            <% pkg.faqs.forEach(function(faq) { %>
            <div class="seo-faq">
              <h3><%= faq.q %></h3>
              <p><%= faq.a %></p>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside class="seo-side-col">

        <div class="seo-sticky-card">
          <h3>Book This Package</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Call or WhatsApp us for pricing and availability. Packages are fully customisable.</p>

          <% if (pkg.pricing && pkg.pricing.length) { %>
          <div class="pkg-price-table">
            <% pkg.pricing.forEach(function(p) { %>
            <div class="pkg-price-row">
              <span><%= p.pax %> · <%= p.vehicle %></span>
              <strong><%= p.price %></strong>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
          <% } %>

          <a href="tel:+919785307799" class="seo-cta-primary" style="display:block; text-align:center; margin-top:1rem;">📞 +91 97853 07799</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/919785307799?text=Hi%2C%20I%20want%20to%20book%20the%20<%= encodeURIComponent(pkg.name) %>." target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="seo-cta-secondary" style="display:block; text-align:center; margin-top:0.75rem;">💬 WhatsApp Us</a>
          <a href="mailto:reservation@rajasthalitours.com" class="seo-cta-secondary" style="display:block; text-align:center; margin-top:0.75rem;">✉️ Email Enquiry</a>

          <div class="seo-trust-row" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <span>🏛️ Govt. Approved</span>
            <span>✈️ IATA Certified</span>
            <span>⭐ 4.8/5 Rating</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <% if (relatedPkgs.length) { %>
        <div class="seo-sticky-card" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
          <h3>Other Packages</h3>
          <% relatedPkgs.forEach(function(rp) { %>
          <a href="/tour-packages/<%= rp.slug %>" class="seo-related-link">
            <strong><%= rp.name %></strong>
            <span><%= rp.duration %></span>
          </a>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="seo-cta-section">
    <div class="seo-container">
      <h2>Customise This Package</h2>
      <p>Every itinerary can be modified — add cities, change hotels, extend duration, upgrade vehicles. Call us for a tailored quote.</p>
      <div class="seo-hero-ctas">
        <a href="tel:+919785307799" class="seo-cta-primary">📞 +91 97853 07799</a>
        <a href="/tour-packages" class="seo-cta-secondary">← All Packages</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/seo-footer') %>
</body>
</html>
